
Convert from String to Numeric time:

		DateTimeFormatter f = DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern("MMMM d, uuuu");
		LocalDate date = LocalDate.parse(str, f);

Convert from Numeric time to String type:
		LocalDate dateFromWebsite = LocalDate.parse(str);
		System.out.println("date: " + dateFromWebsite);
		String dayOfWeek = dateFromWebsite.getDayOfWeek().name();
		System.out.println(dayOfWeek);